repository.name: distributed_minispace
repository.description: Microservices-based social network built with .NET8 and ASP .NET Core Blazor WebAssembly, following distributed DDD principles. Scalable social media application CQRS distributed event-driven solution, utilizing SignalR, .NET ML. Features include choreographical Saga patterns, asynchronous messaging, outbox pattern and distributed event sourcing
